# Mechanics

## About mechanics
Mechanics become harder when dimensions start to shrink. In the LARC VSSS competition, dimensions cannot pass the
75*75*75mm constraint (+5mm if you use uniform ~??), which means that EACH MILIMETER MATTERRRRSSSSS.


## Objective
There are three key elements that must be considered in the space distribution: Motors, Wheels & Useful Space for PCB. 
Other optional elements are: 
- Socket (Hollow space like a 'C' to carry the ball) -HIGHLY RECOMENDABLE-
- Kicker System -NEEDS A LOT OF TIME FOR PREPARATION-
